{"type":"message","id":"348b9101","parentId":"3034ee88","timestamp":"2026-03-20T11:41:45.206Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-03-20 19:41 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 请搜索以下4个领域的最新行业动态（2026年3月）：\n\n1. 企业数字化转型\n2. 智能安防\n3. 网络系统集成\n4. IT运维服务\n\n每个领域搜索1-2条最新资讯，整理成简洁的笔记格式，包括：\n- 信息要点\n- 来源\n- 对道简网络的业务参考价值\n\n完成后返回整理好的内容。"}],"timestamp":1774006905204}}
